description.text:
These are experimental simplified versions of the guide bearings for all three axis on a Mendel type printer.  They are NOT direct replacements and will require other modifications to work.
These are a part of my Mendel/Huxley &quot;remix&quot; currently code named &quot;Mindel&quot; (for MINimal MenDEL) <b >(UPDATE 11/26/10 - project renamed &quot;Integrated Parametric RepRap&quot;)</b>.  These are not ready for prime time but I am releasing them now in the spirit of &quot;release early, release often.&quot;
Follow the progress at <a rel="nofollow" href="http://reprap.org/wiki/Integrated_Parametric_RepRap" >http://reprap.org/wiki/Integrated_Parametric_RepRap</a>

I attempted to sculpt the Groot bust from Guardians of the Galaxy.  It was a pain to detail but it helped give me some more experience in Zbrush.  Anyways, all I have to say is:<br />
&quot;I am Groot.&quot;  
